    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "an1.248-257:1.1",
          "pli": "“Etadaggaṃ, bhikkhave, mama sāvakānaṃ upāsakānaṃ paṭhamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchantānaṃ yadidaṃ tapussabhallikā vāṇijā. (1) ",
          "en": "“The foremost of my laymen in first going for refuge are the merchants Tapussa and Bhallika. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an1.248-257:2.1",
          "pli": "… Dāyakānaṃ yadidaṃ sudatto gahapati anāthapiṇḍiko. (2) ",
          "en": "… as a donor is the householder Sudatta Anāthapiṇḍika. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an1.248-257:3.1",
          "pli": "… Dhammakathikānaṃ yadidaṃ citto gahapati macchikāsaṇḍiko. (3) ",
          "en": "… who speak on the teaching is the householder Citta Macchikāsaṇḍika. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an1.248-257:4.1",
          "pli": "… Catūhi saṅgahavatthūhi parisaṃ saṅgaṇhantānaṃ yadidaṃ hatthako āḷavako. (4) ",
          "en": "… who attract a congregation by the four ways of being inclusive is Hatthaka Āḷavaka. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an1.248-257:5.1",
          "pli": "… Paṇītadāyakānaṃ yadidaṃ mahānāmo sakko. (5) ",
          "en": "… who donate fine things is Mahānāma Sakka. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an1.248-257:6.1",
          "pli": "… Manāpadāyakānaṃ yadidaṃ uggo gahapati vesāliko. (6) ",
          "en": "… who donate nice things is the householder Ugga of Vesālī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an1.248-257:7.1",
          "pli": "… Saṅghupaṭṭhākānaṃ yadidaṃ hatthigāmako uggato gahapati. (7) ",
          "en": "… who attend on the Saṅgha is the householder Uggata of Hatthi Village. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an1.248-257:8.1",
          "pli": "… Aveccappasannānaṃ yadidaṃ sūrambaṭṭho. (8) ",
          "en": "… who have experiential confidence is Sūrambaṭṭha. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an1.248-257:9.1",
          "pli": "… Puggalappasannānaṃ yadidaṃ jīvako komārabhacco. (9) ",
          "en": "… who have confidence in a person is Jīvaka Komārabhacca. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an1.248-257:10.1",
          "pli": "… Vissāsakānaṃ yadidaṃ nakulapitā gahapatī”ti. (10) ",
          "en": "… who are intimate is the householder Nakula’s father.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an1.248-257:10.2",
          "pli": "Vaggo chaṭṭho. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
